HEADWORD: Laurinol
<hw>Lau"ri*nol</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Laurin</ets>
+ <ets>-ol</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Ordinary camphor; -- so
called in allusion to the family name (<fam>Laurace⟦ae⟧</fam>) of the
camphor trees. See <er>Camphor</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

